OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry with sunny spells on
OL,6,FMonday morning. Cloud thickening from
OL,7,Flate morning, with outbreaks of mostly
OL,8,Flight rain spreading east in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Still rather breezy but
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Flight rain this evening, but rain
OL,14,Fslowly easing to become mostly dry by
OL,15,Fdawn. Wind easing. Mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FMostly dry Tuesday morning
OL,18,Fand often cloudy, but some brighter
OL,19,Fspells are possible. Cloud clearing in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon to give longer sunny
OL,21,Fspells. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
