OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,6,Ffog clearing then dry with sunny
OL,7,Fspells Wednesday. Very mild. Breezy
OL,8,Fwith rain or showers Thursday. Mild.
OL,9,FFriday likely wet and windy at first,
OL,10,Fthen cooler with showers later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
